name: Andrew Sq Room Close to T&Shops 2
description:
Single private bedroom available in a 3 bedroom apartment. Large bright room with 2 good sized closets and 2 large windows with lots of natural light, cozy yet spacious with high ceilings.

Great location, less than half mile to the T station with a 10 minute ride via T to downtown and 20 minutes to the airport. Close to the beach, grocery store, BMC, MIT, UMASS.
